27FILE *ipnat_yyin;
28
29#define ishex(c) (ISDIGIT(c) || ((c) >= 'a' && (c) <= 'f') || \
30 ((c) >= 'A' && (c) <= 'F'))
31#define TOOLONG -3
32
33extern int string_start;
34extern int string_end;
35extern char *string_val;
36extern int pos;
37extern int ipnat_yydebug;
38
39char *ipnat_yystr = NULL;
40int ipnat_yytext[YYBUFSIZ+1];
41char ipnat_yychars[YYBUFSIZ+1];
42int ipnat_yylineNum = 1;
43int ipnat_yypos = 0;
44int ipnat_yylast = -1;
45int ipnat_yydictfixed = 0;
46int ipnat_yyexpectaddr = 0;
47int ipnat_yybreakondot = 0;
48int ipnat_yyvarnext = 0;
49int ipnat_yytokentype = 0;
50wordtab_t *ipnat_yywordtab = NULL;
51int ipnat_yysavedepth = 0;
52wordtab_t *ipnat_yysavewords[30];

55static wordtab_t *ipnat_yyfindkey __P((char *));
56static int ipnat_yygetc __P((int));
57static void ipnat_yyunputc __P((int));
58static int ipnat_yyswallow __P((int));
59static char *ipnat_yytexttostr __P((int, int));
60static void ipnat_yystrtotext __P((char *));
61static char *ipnat_yytexttochar __P((void));
62
63static int ipnat_yygetc(docont)
64 int docont;
65{
66 int c;
67
68 if (ipnat_yypos < ipnat_yylast) {
69 c = ipnat_yytext[ipnat_yypos++];
70 if (c == '\n')
71 ipnat_yylineNum++;
72 return c;
73 }
74
75 if (ipnat_yypos == YYBUFSIZ)
76 return TOOLONG;
77
78 if (pos >= string_start && pos <= string_end) {
79 c = string_val[pos - string_start];
80 ipnat_yypos++;
81 } else {
82 c = fgetc(ipnat_yyin);
83 if (docont && (c == '\\')) {
84 c = fgetc(ipnat_yyin);
85 if (c == '\n') {
86 ipnat_yylineNum++;
87 c = fgetc(ipnat_yyin);
88 }
89 }
90 }
91 if (c == '\n')
92 ipnat_yylineNum++;
93 ipnat_yytext[ipnat_yypos++] = c;
94 ipnat_yylast = ipnat_yypos;
95 ipnat_yytext[ipnat_yypos] = '\0';
96
97 return c;
98}
99
100
101static void ipnat_yyunputc(c)
102 int c;
103{
104 if (c == '\n')
105 ipnat_yylineNum--;
106 ipnat_yytext[--ipnat_yypos] = c;
107}
108
109
110static int ipnat_yyswallow(last)
111 int last;
112{
113 int c;
114
115 while (((c = ipnat_yygetc(0)) > '\0') && (c != last))
116 ;
117
118 if (c != EOF)
119 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
120 if (c == last)
121 return 0;
122 return -1;
123}
124
125
126static char *ipnat_yytexttochar()
127{
128 int i;
129
130 for (i = 0; i < ipnat_yypos; i++)
131 ipnat_yychars[i] = (char)(ipnat_yytext[i] & 0xff);
132 ipnat_yychars[i] = '\0';
133 return ipnat_yychars;
134}
135
136
137static void ipnat_yystrtotext(str)
138 char *str;
139{
140 int len;
141 char *s;
142
143 len = strlen(str);
144 if (len > YYBUFSIZ)
145 len = YYBUFSIZ;
146
147 for (s = str; *s != '\0' && len > 0; s++, len--)
148 ipnat_yytext[ipnat_yylast++] = *s;
149 ipnat_yytext[ipnat_yylast] = '\0';
150}
151
152
153static char *ipnat_yytexttostr(offset, max)
154 int offset, max;
155{
156 char *str;
157 int i;
158
159 if ((ipnat_yytext[offset] == '\'' || ipnat_yytext[offset] == '"') &&
160 (ipnat_yytext[offset] == ipnat_yytext[offset + max - 1])) {
161 offset++;
162 max--;
163 }
164
165 if (max > ipnat_yylast)
166 max = ipnat_yylast;
167 str = malloc(max + 1);
168 if (str != NULL) {
169 for (i = offset; i < max; i++)
170 str[i - offset] = (char)(ipnat_yytext[i] & 0xff);
171 str[i - offset] = '\0';
172 }
173 return str;
174}
175
176
177int ipnat_yylex()
178{
179#ifdef USE_INET6
180 static int prior = 0;
181 static int priornum = 0;
182#endif
183 int c, n, isbuilding, rval, lnext, nokey = 0;
184 char *name;
185 int triedv6 = 0;
186
187 isbuilding = 0;
188 lnext = 0;
189 rval = 0;
190
191 if (ipnat_yystr != NULL) {
192 free(ipnat_yystr);
193 ipnat_yystr = NULL;
194 }
195
196nextchar:
197 c = ipnat_yygetc(0);
198 if (ipnat_yydebug > 1)
199 printf("ipnat_yygetc = (%x) %c [%*.*s]\n",
200 c, c, ipnat_yypos, ipnat_yypos, ipnat_yytexttochar());
201
202 switch (c)
203 {
204 case '\n' :
205 lnext = 0;
206 nokey = 0;
207 case '\t' :
208 case '\r' :
209 case ' ' :
210 if (isbuilding == 1) {
211 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
212 goto done;
213 }
214 if (ipnat_yylast > ipnat_yypos) {
215 bcopy(ipnat_yytext + ipnat_yypos, ipnat_yytext,
216 sizeof(ipnat_yytext[0]) * (ipnat_yylast - ipnat_yypos + 1));
217 }
218 ipnat_yylast -= ipnat_yypos;
219 if (ipnat_yyexpectaddr == 2)
220 ipnat_yyexpectaddr = 0;
221 ipnat_yypos = 0;
222 lnext = 0;
223 nokey = 0;
224 goto nextchar;
225
226 case '\\' :
227 if (lnext == 0) {
228 lnext = 1;
229 if (ipnat_yylast == ipnat_yypos) {
230 ipnat_yylast--;
231 ipnat_yypos--;
232 } else
233 ipnat_yypos--;
234 if (ipnat_yypos == 0)
235 nokey = 1;
236 goto nextchar;
237 }
238 break;
239 }
240
241 if (lnext == 1) {
242 lnext = 0;
243 if ((isbuilding == 0) && !ISALNUM(c)) {
244#ifdef USE_INET6
245 prior = c;
246#endif
247 return c;
248 }
249 goto nextchar;
250 }
251
252 switch (c)
253 {
254 case '#' :
255 if (isbuilding == 1) {
256 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
257 goto done;
258 }
259 ipnat_yyswallow('\n');
260 rval = YY_COMMENT;
261 goto done;
262
263 case '$' :
264 if (isbuilding == 1) {
265 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
266 goto done;
267 }
268 n = ipnat_yygetc(0);
269 if (n == '{') {
270 if (ipnat_yyswallow('}') == -1) {
271 rval = -2;
272 goto done;
273 }
274 (void) ipnat_yygetc(0);
275 } else {
276 if (!ISALPHA(n)) {
277 ipnat_yyunputc(n);
278 break;
279 }
280 do {
281 n = ipnat_yygetc(1);
282 } while (ISALPHA(n) || ISDIGIT(n) || n == '_');
283 ipnat_yyunputc(n);
284 }
285
286 name = ipnat_yytexttostr(1, ipnat_yypos); /* skip $ */
287
288 if (name != NULL) {
289 string_val = get_variable(name, NULL, ipnat_yylineNum);
290 free(name);
291 if (string_val != NULL) {
292 name = ipnat_yytexttostr(ipnat_yypos, ipnat_yylast);
293 if (name != NULL) {
294 ipnat_yypos = 0;
295 ipnat_yylast = 0;
296 ipnat_yystrtotext(string_val);
297 ipnat_yystrtotext(name);
298 free(string_val);
299 free(name);
300 goto nextchar;
301 }
302 free(string_val);
303 }
304 }
305 break;
306
307 case '\'':
308 case '"' :
309 if (isbuilding == 1) {
310 goto done;
311 }
312 do {
313 n = ipnat_yygetc(1);
314 if (n == EOF || n == TOOLONG) {
315 rval = -2;
316 goto done;
317 }
318 if (n == '\n') {
319 ipnat_yyunputc(' ');
320 ipnat_yypos++;
321 }
322 } while (n != c);
323 rval = YY_STR;
324 goto done;
325 /* NOTREACHED */
326
327 case EOF :
328 ipnat_yylineNum = 1;
329 ipnat_yypos = 0;
330 ipnat_yylast = -1;
331 ipnat_yyexpectaddr = 0;
332 ipnat_yybreakondot = 0;
333 ipnat_yyvarnext = 0;
334 ipnat_yytokentype = 0;
335 if (ipnat_yydebug)
336 fprintf(stderr, "reset at EOF\n");
337#ifdef USE_INET6
338 prior = 0;
339#endif
340 return 0;
341 }
342
343 if (strchr("=,/;{}()@", c) != NULL) {
344 if (isbuilding == 1) {
345 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
346 goto done;
347 }
348 rval = c;
349 goto done;
350 } else if (c == '.') {
351 if (isbuilding == 0) {
352 rval = c;
353 goto done;
354 }
355 if (ipnat_yybreakondot != 0) {
356 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
357 goto done;
358 }
359 }
360
361 switch (c)
362 {
363 case '-' :
364 n = ipnat_yygetc(0);
365 if (n == '>') {
366 isbuilding = 1;
367 goto done;
368 }
369 ipnat_yyunputc(n);
370 if (ipnat_yyexpectaddr) {
371 if (isbuilding == 1)
372 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
373 else
374 rval = '-';
375 goto done;
376 }
377 if (isbuilding == 1)
378 break;
379 rval = '-';
380 goto done;
381
382 case '!' :
383 if (isbuilding == 1) {
384 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
385 goto done;
386 }
387 n = ipnat_yygetc(0);
388 if (n == '=') {
389 rval = YY_CMP_NE;
390 goto done;
391 }
392 ipnat_yyunputc(n);
393 rval = '!';
394 goto done;
395
396 case '<' :
397 if (ipnat_yyexpectaddr)
398 break;
399 if (isbuilding == 1) {
400 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
401 goto done;
402 }
403 n = ipnat_yygetc(0);
404 if (n == '=') {
405 rval = YY_CMP_LE;
406 goto done;
407 }
408 if (n == '>') {
409 rval = YY_RANGE_OUT;
410 goto done;
411 }
412 ipnat_yyunputc(n);
413 rval = YY_CMP_LT;
414 goto done;
415
416 case '>' :
417 if (ipnat_yyexpectaddr)
418 break;
419 if (isbuilding == 1) {
420 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
421 goto done;
422 }
423 n = ipnat_yygetc(0);
424 if (n == '=') {
425 rval = YY_CMP_GE;
426 goto done;
427 }
428 if (n == '<') {
429 rval = YY_RANGE_IN;
430 goto done;
431 }
432 ipnat_yyunputc(n);
433 rval = YY_CMP_GT;
434 goto done;
435 }
436
437 /*
438 * Now for the reason this is here...IPv6 address parsing.
439 * The longest string we can expect is of this form:
440 * 0000:0000:0000:0000:0000:0000:000.000.000.000
441 * not:
442 * 0000:0000:0000:0000:0000:0000:0000:0000
443 */
444#ifdef USE_INET6
445 if (ipnat_yyexpectaddr != 0 && isbuilding == 0 &&
446 (ishex(c) || isdigit(c) || c == ':')) {
447 char ipv6buf[45 + 1], *s, oc;
448 int start;
449
450buildipv6:
451 start = ipnat_yypos;
452 s = ipv6buf;
453 oc = c;
454
455 if (prior == YY_NUMBER && c == ':') {
456 sprintf(s, "%d", priornum);
457 s += strlen(s);
458 }
459
460 /*
461 * Perhaps we should implement stricter controls on what we
462 * swallow up here, but surely it would just be duplicating
463 * the code in inet_pton() anyway.
464 */
465 do {
466 *s++ = c;
467 c = ipnat_yygetc(1);
468 } while ((ishex(c) || c == ':' || c == '.') &&
469 (s - ipv6buf < 46));
470 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
471 *s = '\0';
472
473 if (inet_pton(AF_INET6, ipv6buf, &ipnat_yylval.ip6) == 1) {
474 rval = YY_IPV6;
475 ipnat_yyexpectaddr = 0;
476 goto done;
477 }
478 ipnat_yypos = start;
479 c = oc;
480 }
481#endif
482
483 if ((c == ':') && (rval != YY_IPV6) && (triedv6 == 0)) {
484#ifdef USE_INET6
485 ipnat_yystr = ipnat_yytexttostr(0, ipnat_yypos - 1);
486 if (ipnat_yystr != NULL) {
487 char *s;
488
489 for (s = ipnat_yystr; *s && ishex(*s); s++)
490 ;
491 if (!*s && *ipnat_yystr) {
492 isbuilding = 0;
493 c = *ipnat_yystr;
494 free(ipnat_yystr);
495 triedv6 = 1;
496 ipnat_yypos = 1;
497 goto buildipv6;
498 }
499 free(ipnat_yystr);
500 }
501#endif
502 if (isbuilding == 1) {
503 ipnat_yyunputc(c);
504 goto done;
505 }
506 rval = ':';
507 goto done;
508 }
509
510 if (isbuilding == 0 && c == '0') {
511 n = ipnat_yygetc(0);
512 if (n == 'x') {
513 do {
514 n = ipnat_yygetc(1);
515 } while (ishex(n));
516 ipnat_yyunputc(n);
517 rval = YY_HEX;
518 goto done;
519 }
520 ipnat_yyunputc(n);
521 }
522
523 /*
524 * No negative numbers with leading - sign..
525 */
526 if (isbuilding == 0 && ISDIGIT(c)) {
527 do {
528 n = ipnat_yygetc(1);
529 } while (ISDIGIT(n));
530 ipnat_yyunputc(n);
531 rval = YY_NUMBER;
532 goto done;
533 }
534
535 isbuilding = 1;
536 goto nextchar;
537
538done:
539 ipnat_yystr = ipnat_yytexttostr(0, ipnat_yypos);
540
541 if (ipnat_yydebug)
542 printf("isbuilding %d ipnat_yyvarnext %d nokey %d fixed %d addr %d\n",
543 isbuilding, ipnat_yyvarnext, nokey, ipnat_yydictfixed, ipnat_yyexpectaddr);
544 if (isbuilding == 1) {
545 wordtab_t *w;
546
547 w = NULL;
548 isbuilding = 0;
549
550 if ((ipnat_yyvarnext == 0) && (nokey == 0)) {
551 w = ipnat_yyfindkey(ipnat_yystr);
552 if (w == NULL && ipnat_yywordtab != NULL && !ipnat_yydictfixed) {
553 ipnat_yyresetdict();
554 w = ipnat_yyfindkey(ipnat_yystr);
555 }
556 } else
557 ipnat_yyvarnext = 0;
558 if (w != NULL)
559 rval = w->w_value;
560 else
561 rval = YY_STR;
562 }
563
564 if (rval == YY_STR) {
565 if (ipnat_yysavedepth > 0 && !ipnat_yydictfixed)
566 ipnat_yyresetdict();
567 if (ipnat_yyexpectaddr != 0)
568 ipnat_yyexpectaddr = 0;
569 }
570
571 ipnat_yytokentype = rval;
572
573 if (ipnat_yydebug)
574 printf("lexed(%s) %d,%d,%d [%d,%d,%d] => %d @%d\n",
575 ipnat_yystr, isbuilding, ipnat_yyexpectaddr, ipnat_yysavedepth,
576 string_start, string_end, pos, rval, ipnat_yysavedepth);
577
578 switch (rval)
579 {
580 case YY_NUMBER :
581 sscanf(ipnat_yystr, "%u", &ipnat_yylval.num);
582 break;
583
584 case YY_HEX :
585 sscanf(ipnat_yystr, "0x%x", (u_int *)&ipnat_yylval.num);
586 break;
587
588 case YY_STR :
589 ipnat_yylval.str = strdup(ipnat_yystr);
590 break;
591
592 default :
593 break;
594 }
595
596 if (ipnat_yylast > 0) {
597 bcopy(ipnat_yytext + ipnat_yypos, ipnat_yytext,
598 sizeof(ipnat_yytext[0]) * (ipnat_yylast - ipnat_yypos + 1));
599 ipnat_yylast -= ipnat_yypos;
600 ipnat_yypos = 0;
601 }
602
603#ifdef USE_INET6
604 if (rval == YY_NUMBER)
605 priornum = ipnat_yylval.num;
606 prior = rval;
607#endif
608 return rval;
609}

612static wordtab_t *ipnat_yyfindkey(key)
613 char *key;
614{
615 wordtab_t *w;
616
617 if (ipnat_yywordtab == NULL)
618 return NULL;
619
620 for (w = ipnat_yywordtab; w->w_word != 0; w++)
621 if (strcasecmp(key, w->w_word) == 0)
622 return w;
623 return NULL;
624}
625
626
627char *ipnat_yykeytostr(num)
628 int num;
629{
630 wordtab_t *w;
631
632 if (ipnat_yywordtab == NULL)
633 return "<unknown>";
634
635 for (w = ipnat_yywordtab; w->w_word; w++)
636 if (w->w_value == num)
637 return w->w_word;
638 return "<unknown>";
639}
640
641
642wordtab_t *ipnat_yysettab(words)
643 wordtab_t *words;
644{
645 wordtab_t *save;
646
647 save = ipnat_yywordtab;
648 ipnat_yywordtab = words;
649 return save;
650}

652
653void ipnat_yyerror(msg)
654 char *msg;
655{
656 char *txt, letter[2];
657 int freetxt = 0;
658
659 if (ipnat_yytokentype < 256) {
660 letter[0] = ipnat_yytokentype;
661 letter[1] = '\0';
662 txt = letter;
663 } else if (ipnat_yytokentype == YY_STR || ipnat_yytokentype == YY_HEX ||
664 ipnat_yytokentype == YY_NUMBER) {
665 if (ipnat_yystr == NULL) {
666 txt = ipnat_yytexttostr(ipnat_yypos, YYBUFSIZ);
667 freetxt = 1;
668 } else
669 txt = ipnat_yystr;
670 } else {
671 txt = ipnat_yykeytostr(ipnat_yytokentype);
672 }
673 fprintf(stderr, "%s error at \"%s\", line %d\n", msg, txt, ipnat_yylineNum);
674 if (freetxt == 1)
675 free(txt);
676 exit(1);
677}

679
680void ipnat_yysetfixeddict(newdict)
681 wordtab_t *newdict;
682{
683 if (ipnat_yydebug)
684 printf("ipnat_yysetfixeddict(%lx)\n", (u_long)newdict);
685
686 if (ipnat_yysavedepth == sizeof(ipnat_yysavewords)/sizeof(ipnat_yysavewords[0])) {
687 fprintf(stderr, "%d: at maximum dictionary depth\n",
688 ipnat_yylineNum);
689 return;
690 }
691
692 ipnat_yysavewords[ipnat_yysavedepth++] = ipnat_yysettab(newdict);
693 if (ipnat_yydebug)
694 printf("ipnat_yysavedepth++ => %d\n", ipnat_yysavedepth);
695 ipnat_yydictfixed = 1;
696}
697
698
699void ipnat_yysetdict(newdict)
700 wordtab_t *newdict;
701{
702 if (ipnat_yydebug)
703 printf("ipnat_yysetdict(%lx)\n", (u_long)newdict);
704
705 if (ipnat_yysavedepth == sizeof(ipnat_yysavewords)/sizeof(ipnat_yysavewords[0])) {
706 fprintf(stderr, "%d: at maximum dictionary depth\n",
707 ipnat_yylineNum);
708 return;
709 }
710
711 ipnat_yysavewords[ipnat_yysavedepth++] = ipnat_yysettab(newdict);
712 if (ipnat_yydebug)
713 printf("ipnat_yysavedepth++ => %d\n", ipnat_yysavedepth);
714}
715
716void ipnat_yyresetdict()
717{
718 if (ipnat_yydebug)
719 printf("ipnat_yyresetdict(%d)\n", ipnat_yysavedepth);
720 if (ipnat_yysavedepth > 0) {
721 ipnat_yysettab(ipnat_yysavewords[--ipnat_yysavedepth]);
722 if (ipnat_yydebug)
723 printf("ipnat_yysavedepth-- => %d\n", ipnat_yysavedepth);
724 }
725 ipnat_yydictfixed = 0;
726}

730#ifdef TEST_LEXER
731int main(argc, argv)
732 int argc;
733 char *argv[];
734{
735 int n;
736
737 ipnat_yyin = stdin;
738
739 while ((n = ipnat_yylex()) != 0)
740 printf("%d.n = %d [%s] %d %d\n",
741 ipnat_yylineNum, n, ipnat_yystr, ipnat_yypos, ipnat_yylast);
742}
